Package entities

Class OfficerApplication

java.lang.Object
entities.OfficerApplication
public class OfficerApplication extends Object
Represents an application made by an officer for a specific project. The officer can apply for a project, and the application contains details about the applicant's ID, the project's name, and the current status of the application.
